# 6c2c6e9051f1426cbb8a14a36c552637
msgid "The ``Chef::Platform`` class maps providers to platforms (and platform versions). At the beginning of every |chef client| run, |ohai| verifies the ``platform`` and ``platform_version`` attributes on each node. The |chef client| then uses those values to identify the correct provider, build an instance of that provider, identify the current state of the resource, do the specified action, and then mark the resource as updated (if changes were made)."
msgstr ""

